body:
Enemy mid laner picks {{champion:45}} , as a response I pick {{champion:91}}.

The old strategy against Veigar was EWQ or EQWQ (combo based off how far he was from his turret). 

With Talon&#039;s new passive and his new Q = old EQ, I was like &quot;ez lane for me.&quot;

On top of the super hard range nerf, you should have seen the look on my face when Veigar used Event Horizon, me pressing Q on to Veigar then... STUNNED MID &quot;LEAP&quot; 
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}} 

E used to be a &quot;blink&quot;, so whenever a {{champion:45}} {{champion:30}} {{champion:268}} put up their walls, I would just appear behind them. Now you&#039;re telling me Veigar stuns me, Karthus gets his debuff (meaning he&#039;ll end up melting me with his passive after I kill him) and Azir&#039;s wall will knock me back!

FIX! FIX! FIX! I want Talon&#039;s blink back!
